"{\"uid\": \"cyclingnews.com-news-how-to-watch-olympics-track-cycling-live-streams-at-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A guide to watching all the action on the velodrome from August 5-11  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are now subscribed  Your newsletter sign-up was successful  We have already had cycling action across three separate disciplines at theParis Olympic Games, but for many, the track is home to the best of the lot, a week-long sm\\u00f6rg\\u00e5sbord of thrilling competition.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spanning seven days from August 5-11, here's how to watch an Olympics 2024 Track Cycling live stream.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Track cycling takes place on an indoor velodrome, an oval-shaped 250-metre track made of wood, with straight sides and steep bankings at either end.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are numerous race formats but they are broadly split into two sections: Sprint and Endurance.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.243755528253281e-21, \"text\": \"Sprint\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sprint events feature short sharp efforts from impossibly muscular riders able to put out huge power, while the endurance events take place over a longer time for those with leaner physiques.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are six events for both the men's and women's fields, so 12 gold medals up for grabs in Paris.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.983858212120919e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the sprinting side, there is the Individual Sprint, Team Sprint, and Keirin, while on the endurance end there is the Team Pursuit, Madison, and Omnium.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sprint, Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\"}, {\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sprint, Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\"}, {\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.243755528253281e-21, \"text\": \"Sprint\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 1267, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.717934022883868e-62, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.